snippet.title: Goblins of Elderstone - Launch Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Get Goblins Of Elderstone on STEAM: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/693580/Goblins_of_Elderstone/

Join the tribe:
🌱https://twitter.com/GoblinsOfElder
🫐https://www.instagram.com/goblinsofelder/
🔥https://www.facebook.com/goblinsofelderstone
⚔️https://www.tiktok.com/@goblinsofelder
🍻https://discord.gg/X2K2sEZbKz

Goblins of Elderstone brings a unique and chaotic twist to the city-building genre - it’s a Goblin Tribe Simulator! Nurture your tiny clan as it grows to stand against the other races and even the gods. Rule over the chaos and feed the growing goblin war machine by raiding dungeons and villages.
